  "body": "Desktop Remix IDE 1.3.6 (1.3.6.1000) / 1.3.7 (1.3.7)\r\n![image](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/assets/16279944/a33446e2-cb53-43af-a5af-babbccffb0bb)\r\n\r\nBug in remix-project/libs/remixd/src/services/remixdClient.ts\r\n[this.watcher = chokidar.watch(path, { depth: 2, ignorePermissionErrors: true })](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/blob/7ad68aaf8a49dea2c2a1b03832dcacd2fe8ff3b0/libs/remixd/src/services/remixdClient.ts#L254)\r\n\r\n1. This dependency checks all files every 100ms.\r\n\r\n2. path - '/'. Checking for file updates works throughout the system.\r\n![image](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/assets/16279944/c052d778-c64c-444c-bad3-ddd33464804e)\r\n\r\n3. Tries request for permissions to access photos, contacts, etc.\r\n![image](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/assets/16279944/673f634d-a959-4acf-b452-404587b14aa9)\r\n![image](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/assets/16279944/c20827e5-a259-4b30-a4b3-3271dba3ebf9)\r\n\r\nIt is necessary to make it possible to work only with the project directory.\r\nFix method:\r\n1. Increase time between file polls via interval, binaryInterval https://www.npmjs.com/package/chokidar\r\n2. Before connecting remixd, ask the user for a working directory and pass it to remixd.",
